"CMD+SHIFT+P" > ">Preferences: Open Keyboard Shortcuts (JSON)" > copy+paste the below

Note ^^ there's a default keyboard short cuts file that is not editable. you want the editable one instead.
####

[
  {
    "key": "cmd+[",
    "command": "workbench.action.previousEditor"
  },
  {
    "key": "cmd+]",
    "command": "workbench.action.nextEditor"
  },
  {
    "key": "cmd+1",
    "command": "workbench.action.openEditorAtIndex1"
  },
  {
    "key": "cmd+2",
    "command": "workbench.action.openEditorAtIndex2"
  },
  {
    "key": "cmd+3",
    "command": "workbench.action.openEditorAtIndex3"
  },
